71beb70e-7d30-4d48-aa39-c3c329355002.title: Ajjat
71beb70e-7d30-4d48-aa39-c3c329355002.text:
Greetings, fellow warrior. I am Ajjat, former black
knight and now training officer here in the warrior
guild.

7f9e161c-fb1c-4f62-980a-dbfa2bd5df7e.title: Ajjat
7f9e161c-fb1c-4f62-980a-dbfa2bd5df7e.text:
Ah, but I can see you are already a master in the fine
art of attacking, perhaps you have come to me to
purchase a Cape of Attack, and thus join the elite few
who have mastered this exacting skill?

6ec2520a-ebff-4d76-9726-fd6f35f00987.title: Ajjat
6ec2520a-ebff-4d76-9726-fd6f35f00987.text:
When wearing this cape, Kamfreena will recognize your
ability and allow you to access her Cyclopes without the
need for guild tokens.

options.text: Black Knight? Why are you here?
What's the Dummy Room all about?
May I claim my tokens please?

70d4a382-68d5-4db2-876a-8576e9301c83.title: <player>
70d4a382-68d5-4db2-876a-8576e9301c83.text: What's the Dummy Room all about?

8f1a4c03-eca4-4fd4-844e-9fd90ae9da9f.title: Ajjat
8f1a4c03-eca4-4fd4-844e-9fd90ae9da9f.text:
Ahh yes, the dummies. Another ingenious invention of
the noble Dwarf Gamfred. They're mechanical you see
and pop up out of the floor. You have to hit them with
the correct attack mode before they disappear again.

e494e39d-2111-4eaf-9eec-90598b96029e.title: <player>
e494e39d-2111-4eaf-9eec-90598b96029e.text: So how do I tell which one is which?

e75f4aab-6363-4b20-a4d9-4583931fc77a.title: Ajjat
e75f4aab-6363-4b20-a4d9-4583931fc77a.text:
There are two different ways. One indication is their
colour, the other is the pose and weapons they are
holding, for instance, the one holding daggers you will
need to hit with a piercing attack.

8c7b9b9c-f891-4f0f-8c40-f8868fc67219.title: Ajjat
8c7b9b9c-f891-4f0f-8c40-f8868fc67219.text:
In the room you will find a poster on the wall which
can help you recognise each different dummy.

773944b0-500b-47cb-81f5-c5f223fb98ad.title: Ajjat
773944b0-500b-47cb-81f5-c5f223fb98ad.text:
Indeed, you may find that you need several weapons to
be successful 100% of the time, but keep trying. The
weapons shop upstairs may help you there.

d852993b-0f37-48c7-9469-972e5695a7a1.title: <player>
d852993b-0f37-48c7-9469-972e5695a7a1.text: Black Knight? Why are you here?

4461e5ab-8e67-4727-8b12-1b27a83a609b.title: Ajjat
4461e5ab-8e67-4727-8b12-1b27a83a609b.text:
Indeed I was, however their... methods... did not match
with my ideals.. so I left. Harrallak, recognising my
talent as a warrior, took me in and offered me a job
here.

66a612fa-6a0f-41c1-ae01-478495df620c.title: <player>
66a612fa-6a0f-41c1-ae01-478495df620c.text: Hmm... well if Harrallak trusts you, I guess I can.

93b60b1e-0376-4d30-b4fe-265e75b5869b.title: Ajjat
93b60b1e-0376-4d30-b4fe-265e75b5869b.text: Farewell warrior. Stay away from the dark side.

9bc019a6-d27f-428e-9278-8c6020ae1d6e.title: <player>
9bc019a6-d27f-428e-9278-8c6020ae1d6e.text: May I claim my tokens please?

3727b8c6-3cb7-4fe0-a984-47d1680400ab.title: Ajjat
3727b8c6-3cb7-4fe0-a984-47d1680400ab.text:
I'm afraid you have not earned any tokens yet. Try
some of the activities around the guild to earn some.

a9bb5965-82c6-4317-8ed0-c3b57c4e274f.title: <player>
a9bb5965-82c6-4317-8ed0-c3b57c4e274f.text: Ok, I'll go see what I can find.
